<a name="religion">

<h2 align="center">Religion</h2>

<p><img SRC="../../images/culture/euph-kr.jpg" hspace="20" vspace="10" BORDER="1"
align="right" alt="The cross of Saint Efrasinnia" width="140" height="300"> 

<ul>
  <li></a><a href="../../culture1/religion/Religion.html">Religion in Belarus </a>- short
    account of Belarusian religious path </li>
  <li><a href="../../culture1/religion/BAOC.html">Belarusian Autocephalous Orthodox Church: A
    Brief History </a>- by D.Zielenka </li>
  <li><a href="../../culture1/religion/icons/index.html">Belarusian Icon-Painting </a>- some
    pictures of original school of sacral paintings by Mikalaj Karelin </li>
</ul>

